\begin_layout Theorem
(Tauber, 1897).
 设序列
\begin_inset Formula $\left\{ a_{k}\right\} $
\end_inset

为复数列, 假设
\begin_inset Formula 
\[
A(r)=\sum_{k=0}^{+\infty}a_{k}r^{k}
\]

\end_inset

对于任意的
\begin_inset Formula $r\in(0,1)$
\end_inset

收敛.
 若
\begin_inset Formula $A(r)\to A$
\end_inset

, 
\begin_inset Formula $r\to1^{-}$
\end_inset

.
 且
\begin_inset Formula $ka_{k}=o(1)$
\end_inset

, 则有
\begin_inset Formula 
\[
\sum_{k=0}^{+\infty}a_{k}=A.
\]

\end_inset


\end_layout

\begin_layout Paragraph
证明: 
\end_layout

\begin_layout Standard
因为
\begin_inset Formula $\sum a_{k}r^{k}\to A$
\end_inset

, 
\begin_inset Formula $r\to1^{-}$
\end_inset

, 只需证
\begin_inset Formula 
\[
\sum_{k=0}^{N}a_{k}-\sum_{k=0}^{+\infty}a_{k}r^{k}\rightarrow0
\]

\end_inset

沿着
\begin_inset Formula $r=1-\frac{1}{N}$
\end_inset

, 
\begin_inset Formula $N\to+\infty$
\end_inset

成立即可.
 对于任意的
\begin_inset Formula $\epsilon>0$
\end_inset

, 存在
\begin_inset Formula $K$
\end_inset

使得, 只要
\begin_inset Formula $k>K$
\end_inset

, 就有
\begin_inset Formula $\left|ka_{k}\right|>\epsilon$
\end_inset

.
 于是记
\begin_inset Formula 
\[
\begin{aligned}\sum_{k=0}^{N}a_{k}-\sum_{k=0}^{+\infty}a_{k}r^{k} & =\sum_{k=0}^{K}a_{k}\left(1-r^{k}\right)+\sum_{k=K+1}^{N}a_{k}\left(1-r^{k}\right)-\sum_{k=N+1}^{+\infty}a_{k}r^{k}\\
 & =I_{1}+I_{2}+I_{3}.
\end{aligned}
\]

\end_inset

显然, 当
\begin_inset Formula $N\to+\infty$
\end_inset

时有
\begin_inset Formula $I_{1}\to0$
\end_inset

.
 对于
\begin_inset Formula $I_{2}$
\end_inset

, 有
\begin_inset Formula 
\[
\begin{aligned}\left|I_{2}\right| & \leq(1-r)\sum_{k=K+1}^{N}\left|a_{k}\right|\left(1+\cdots+r^{k-1}\right)\\
 & \leq(1-r)\sum_{k=K+1}^{N}\left|ka_{k}\right|\\
 & \leq(1-r)N\epsilon\leq\epsilon,
\end{aligned}
\]

\end_inset

注意上式中的
\begin_inset Formula $r$
\end_inset

是沿着
\begin_inset Formula $1-\frac{1}{N}$
\end_inset

趋向于
\begin_inset Formula $1$
\end_inset

.
 对于
\begin_inset Formula $I_{3}$
\end_inset

, 有
\begin_inset Formula 
\[
\left|I_{3}\right|\leq\sum_{k=N+1}^{+\infty}\left|ka_{k}\right|\frac{r^{k}}{k}<\frac{\epsilon}{N+1}\sum_{k=0}^{+\infty}r^{k}<\epsilon.
\]

\end_inset


\end_layout

\begin_layout Standard
Littlewood, 1911年将上面定理的
\begin_inset Formula $o(1)$
\end_inset

弱化为
\begin_inset Formula $\mathcal{O}(1)$
\end_inset

.
 Tauberian定理一般用来从级数的Abel可和性推出实可和性.
\end_layout

